    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >什么是SokoChess White？</h2>SokoChess White是一款独特的游戏，您必须运用智慧来挑战每个关卡，在棋盘上移动和推动棋子来到达目的地。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >推动您的棋子</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/2c52880c69f372b0727c5f7a13463b39.poster.avif?t=1757579636\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/2c52880c69f372b0727c5f7a13463b39.webm?t=1757579636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/2c52880c69f372b0727c5f7a13463b39.mp4?t=1757579636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每个关卡的目标是让所有白色棋子到达目的地。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不仅仅是国际象棋</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/c8f425849ac0fa6f1c272e8912d8dd34.poster.avif?t=1757579636\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/c8f425849ac0fa6f1c272e8912d8dd34.webm?t=1757579636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/c8f425849ac0fa6f1c272e8912d8dd34.mp4?t=1757579636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>请运用棋子绕过各种独特的障碍！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/64637d6b76f8def5387b3abc96584a15.avif?t=1757579636\" width=620 height=84 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 70 个独家制作的关卡<br></li><li> 无限撤消<br></li><li> 不喜欢您正在玩的关卡？ 跳过它！<br></li><li> 您不会在国际象棋中看到的拼图元素<br></li><li> 结合国际象棋和推箱子的独特玩法</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验前所未有的国际象棋玩法！</h2>",
